{"word":"H1891 - הָבַל - hâbal - haw-bal' - Be vain - வீணாயிரு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>הָבַל"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hâbal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>haw-bal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be vain / வீணாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வீணாகு, பெருமை பாராட்டு, வீணராய்போ, வீண்பெருமை, கொள்ளும்படி செய்,"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to act emptily, to become vain, to be vain"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to become vain"},{"paragraph":"2) to be utterly vain (with the cognate accusative)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cause to become vain"},{"paragraph":"2) to fill with vain hopes"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>be vain</i> in act, word, or expectation; specifically to <i>lead astray: - </i>be (become, make) vain."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1891 - הָבַל - hâbal - haw-bal'/1891\">H1891</a>, <a href=\"#/H1892 - הֶבֶל - hebel - heh'bel/1892\">H1892</a>"}]}